<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone, get up!</font>

3
00:00:05,910 --> 00:00:09,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have an emergency! 
Arm yourselves and get ready!</font>

4
00:00:09,590 --> 00:00:10,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

5
00:00:10,630 --> 00:00:12,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's still dark out.</font>

6
00:00:12,490 --> 00:00:13,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up?</font>

7
00:00:14,190 --> 00:00:16,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An Aizu messenger just arrived.</font>

8
00:00:16,890 --> 00:00:19,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A crisis has broken out at the palace.</font>

9
00:00:19,360 --> 00:00:20,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At the palace?</font>

10
00:00:20,420 --> 00:00:21,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with your hair?</font>

11
00:00:22,090 --> 00:00:24,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean the palace 
where the emperor lives?</font>

12
00:00:24,970 --> 00:00:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And arm ourselves with what?</font>

13
00:00:29,520 --> 00:00:31,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Breastplates fastened?</font>

14
00:00:31,040 --> 00:00:32,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Put on full armor!</font>

15
00:00:32,420 --> 00:00:33,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't forget headgear!</font>

16
00:00:34,120 --> 00:00:36,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knew we had all this stuff
 ready in the storehouse?</font>

17
00:00:36,900 --> 00:00:38,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Serizawa's doing.</font>

18
00:00:39,030 --> 00:00:41,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. Where is Serizawa-san?</font>

19
00:00:41,530 --> 00:00:44,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Confining himself, stupid.
Forget that guy.</font>

20
00:00:45,020 --> 00:00:47,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Men! I trust you are prepared!</font>

21
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:49,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">March!</font>

