00:00:56,370 --> 00:01:04,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia">{\an8}<b><font size="60"><font color="#0c49ea">Blue Miburo</font></font></b></font></font>

40
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:34,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Miburo will stand guard
 inside the palace.</font>

41
00:02:34,470 --> 00:02:37,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll enter through the 
Hamaguri Gate on the west side.</font>

42
00:02:37,190 --> 00:02:39,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean we'll be fighting 
<i>inside</i> the palace?</font>

43
00:02:39,780 --> 00:02:42,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But who in the world is attacking it?</font>

44
00:02:42,510 --> 00:02:43,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Choshu, apparently.</font>

45
00:02:44,050 --> 00:02:47,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Choshu? Weren't they in charge
 of palace security?</font>

46
00:02:47,870 --> 00:02:50,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, but it seems they've been driven out.</font>

47
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:53,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They got kicked out? What for?</font>

48
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:55,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That I do not know.</font>

49
00:02:56,100 --> 00:02:59,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm told Aizu and Satsuma
are now sharing the duty.</font>

50
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:05,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, my sister lives in the house
 of a court noble. Will she be all right?</font>

51
00:03:06,070 --> 00:03:08,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yeah, that's the question.</i></font>

52
00:03:09,060 --> 00:03:12,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She didn't mention the Choshu 
faction specifically, but still...</i></font>

53
00:03:16,180 --> 00:03:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get out, Choshu!</font>

54
00:03:17,900 --> 00:03:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We won't allow you 
to set one foot past us!</font>

55
00:03:19,930 --> 00:03:21,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You dumb Satsuma bumpkins!</font>

56
00:03:21,350 --> 00:03:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let us in!</font>

57
00:03:27,060 --> 00:03:27,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who're you?</font>

58
00:03:29,650 --> 00:03:31,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't recognize any of you.</font>

59
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:33,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your domain and 
under whose banner?</font>

60
00:03:33,690 --> 00:03:35,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We serve Aizu.</font>

61
00:03:35,570 --> 00:03:37,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're</i> from Aizu.</font>

62
00:03:37,570 --> 00:03:38,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, if you'll only—</font>

63
00:03:38,670 --> 00:03:41,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget it. Just go. We're not 
opening this gate for anyone.</font>

64
00:03:43,300 --> 00:03:46,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you know why they call this the 
Hamaguri Gate, like the clams?</font>

65
00:03:46,370 --> 00:03:46,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

66
00:03:46,760 --> 00:03:50,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because it has remained shut except for one 
time during the great fire in the Hoei era.</font>

67
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:53,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like they say, "A clam only opens
 its mouth when it's burning."</font>

68
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:57,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That ought to tell you how tightly
 this gate stays closed.</font>

69
00:03:57,860 --> 00:04:00,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does it truly open so rarely?</font>

70
00:04:00,540 --> 00:04:02,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems there's been a miscommunication.</font>

71
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:06,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Lord of Aizu has formally instructed us
to stand guard inside the palace.</font>

72
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What'd you say?</font>

73
00:04:10,740 --> 00:04:11,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Toshi.</font>

74
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:15,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We, the Mibu Roshigumi, 
serve under the patronage of Aizu!</font>

75
00:04:16,050 --> 00:04:18,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is anyone here willing 
to discuss matters reasonably—</font>

76
00:04:18,840 --> 00:04:20,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold your tongue.</font>

77
00:04:20,370 --> 00:04:22,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get out of here. Shoo.</font>

78
00:04:22,890 --> 00:04:24,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Move, Hasumukai.</font>

79
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:28,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget that blockhead.
Just march on through.</font>

80
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:35,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So much for that plan.</font>

81
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you stupid?</font>

82
00:04:36,910 --> 00:04:38,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well. We'll come again.</font>

83
00:04:39,380 --> 00:04:40,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

84
00:04:41,290 --> 00:04:45,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We cannot tolerate mistakes. 
I sympathize with their position.</font>

85
00:04:49,370 --> 00:04:50,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're leaving?</font>

86
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:52,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}That wasn't supposed to be the deal.</font>

87
00:04:50,540 --> 00:04:52,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After marching all the way here?</font>

88
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a waste of a trip.</font>

89
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:57,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, Sir Kondo!</font>

90
00:05:07,550 --> 00:05:09,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not the way.</font>

91
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa-san.</font>

92
00:05:12,700 --> 00:05:13,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa-san.</font>

93
00:05:14,490 --> 00:05:15,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Se—</font>

94
00:05:15,500 --> 00:05:17,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa-sensei!</font>

95
00:05:18,080 --> 00:05:19,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your confinement?</font>

96
00:05:20,540 --> 00:05:21,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I ended it.</font>

97
00:05:21,970 --> 00:05:23,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just like that?</font>

98
00:05:25,010 --> 00:05:26,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch.</font>

99
00:05:29,990 --> 00:05:33,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Who the hell are you?
D-Don't come any closer!</font>

100
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn you!</font>

101
00:05:40,550 --> 00:05:41,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

102
00:05:42,850 --> 00:05:44,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You point your spears at <i>me?</i></font>

103
00:05:44,860 --> 00:05:46,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-A fan?</font>

104
00:05:46,860 --> 00:05:53,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, we must draw our swords in kind.
 But remember, you drew first.</font>

105
00:05:55,090 --> 00:05:58,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll rout every last one of you.</font>

106
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:03,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but we're under 
the patronage of Aizu.</font>

107
00:06:03,050 --> 00:06:06,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're drawing your swords 
against the Imperial Palace,</font>

108
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:09,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">does that mean Aizu's rebelling
 against the emperor?</font>

109
00:06:10,130 --> 00:06:11,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Wha—</font>

110
00:06:11,470 --> 00:06:13,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You imbecile!</font>

111
00:06:13,130 --> 00:06:17,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't you even tell friend from foe?!</font>

112
00:06:17,110 --> 00:06:20,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you want to turn 
your own lord into a rebel?</font>

113
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:22,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you even <i>trying</i> 
to defend our nation?</font>

114
00:06:22,930 --> 00:06:24,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wake up!</font>

115
00:06:27,590 --> 00:06:28,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let us through.</font>

116
00:06:33,780 --> 00:06:35,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's clear who's more resourceful.</i></font>

117
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:38,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-Let them through!</font>

118
00:06:45,010 --> 00:06:46,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The hamaguri clam...</font>

119
00:06:46,100 --> 00:06:52,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sir Kondo, that mob probably 
knew to expect the Miburo.</font>

120
00:06:53,510 --> 00:06:56,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They just wanted to push you around.</font>

121
00:06:54,940 --> 00:06:59,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}That guy's huge. I can't stand him.</font>

122
00:06:56,640 --> 00:07:00,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They no doubt thought your duty 
was more important than theirs.</font>

123
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:05,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you think you're in the right,
 stop for no one.</font>

124
00:07:06,010 --> 00:07:12,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The least the leader of an army 
ought to do is keep his men safe.</font>

125
00:07:14,990 --> 00:07:18,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa-sensei's back, and how!</font>

126
00:07:18,010 --> 00:07:20,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave it to a real samurai.</font>

127
00:07:20,140 --> 00:07:22,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where would the Miburo be without you?</font>

128
00:07:24,130 --> 00:07:25,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't lead you wrong.</font>

129
00:07:25,540 --> 00:07:27,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You're our daimyojin!</font>

130
00:07:27,380 --> 00:07:28,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You're our god!</font>

131
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Is he incredible or what?</font>

132
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Daimyojin!</font>

133
00:07:28,860 --> 00:07:29,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's unbelievable.</i></font>

134
00:07:31,030 --> 00:07:33,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've said what I needed to say.</i></font>

135
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:36,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's enough.</i></font>

136
00:07:37,990 --> 00:07:42,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The disturbance would become 
known as "the 8-18 Coup."</i></font>

137
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:46,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Although it involved no major battles,</i></font>

138
00:07:46,870 --> 00:07:51,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>its ripples manifested in unexpected ways, 
even within the Miburo.</i></font>

139
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:01,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Hasumukai!</font>

140
00:08:02,030 --> 00:08:03,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take you on.</font>

141
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:10,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, my bad. I mixed 'em up.</font>

142
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:14,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, Hasumukai!</font>

143
00:08:15,150 --> 00:08:18,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go out on patrol. 
It's an important job.</font>

144
00:08:19,210 --> 00:08:20,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

145
00:08:20,790 --> 00:08:21,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

146
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:25,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something just seems off 
about Hasumukai-san lately.</font>

147
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:30,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The truth is...</i></font>

148
00:08:31,650 --> 00:08:34,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm a Choshu samurai 
who's infiltrated the Miburo.</i></font>

149
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:40,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The fight at the palace changed 
the balance of power overnight.</i></font>

150
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:45,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All of my fellow Choshu 
samurai left Kyoto.</i></font>

151
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:50,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If the truth about me gets out...</i></font>

152
00:08:50,420 --> 00:08:52,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, sorry about that.</font>

153
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:55,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for the holdup. 
I've got a case of the runs.</font>

154
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:56,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's fine.</font>

155
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:03,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Lord of Choshu's residence? 
It looks completely deserted.</font>

156
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:05,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It makes sense, though.</font>

157
00:09:06,140 --> 00:09:09,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say he was plotting to abduct
the emperor and do bad stuff.</font>

158
00:09:09,900 --> 00:09:14,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No. We wanted His Imperial Majesty 
to lead us and expel the barbarians.</i></font>

159
00:09:15,610 --> 00:09:18,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>For Choshu, and for all of Japan.</i></font>

160
00:09:20,030 --> 00:09:22,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Root them out and string them up.</font>

161
00:09:25,260 --> 00:09:28,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Miburo earned praise for 
their performance at the palace,</i></font>

162
00:09:28,510 --> 00:09:31,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and now they're all fired up over
hunting down Choshu stragglers.</i></font>

163
00:09:31,550 --> 00:09:32,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Please come in.</font>

164
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:37,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shinpachi won't hang out 
with me lately, you know?</font>

165
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:38,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

166
00:09:38,660 --> 00:09:41,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My men don't take me seriously, either.</font>

167
00:09:41,130 --> 00:09:42,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, gimme that broth.</font>

168
00:09:42,950 --> 00:09:44,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

169
00:09:44,450 --> 00:09:47,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we've gotta round up 
those Choshu extremists.</font>

170
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:49,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't let bad guys go free.</font>

171
00:09:50,140 --> 00:09:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My superior is compassionate, 
craves company,</i></font>

172
00:09:53,280 --> 00:09:55,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and when convinced, 
he charges in headlong.</i></font>

173
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:59,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He'll be the first to come for my head
 if my secret gets out.</i></font>

174
00:10:02,220 --> 00:10:03,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it!</font>

175
00:10:03,070 --> 00:10:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He got us!</font>

176
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where'd he go?</font>

177
00:10:05,190 --> 00:10:06,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Find him!</font>

178
00:10:06,350 --> 00:10:09,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you find him, you can kill him! 
The reward is yours.</font>

179
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:10,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

180
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:13,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hasumukai! You go that way!</font>

181
00:10:13,150 --> 00:10:13,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

182
00:10:14,780 --> 00:10:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>T-Talk about a bad joke. 
No way am I finding anyone.</i></font>

183
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>P-Please let no one be in here.</i></font>

184
00:10:29,190 --> 00:10:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't shout, stupid.</i></font>

185
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:33,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You found him?</font>

186
00:10:35,450 --> 00:10:36,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well done.</font>

187
00:10:36,980 --> 00:10:38,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, kill him!</font>

188
00:10:38,210 --> 00:10:39,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take vengeance!</font>

189
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:41,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get him! Get him!</font>

190
00:10:41,750 --> 00:10:45,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Go on! Finish him off! Hurry up!</font>

191
00:10:44,740 --> 00:10:46,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This man is me.</i></font>

192
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:51,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I'd stayed in Kyoto on the Choshu side,
 it could've been me in his place.</i></font>

193
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:54,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do it.</font>

194
00:10:57,980 --> 00:10:58,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hey, you...</font>

195
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:01,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forgive me.</font>

196
00:11:04,460 --> 00:11:05,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I missed?</font>

197
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:14,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Th-This couldn't be worse.</i></font>

198
00:11:25,350 --> 00:11:28,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did good yesterday, Hasumukai.</font>

199
00:11:28,660 --> 00:11:29,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

200
00:11:30,430 --> 00:11:32,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheer up.</font>

201
00:11:32,090 --> 00:11:35,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll treat you to soba noodles. 
Just gimme your broth, okay?</font>

202
00:11:37,270 --> 00:11:39,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why is he so nice to me, of all people?</i></font>

203
00:11:41,210 --> 00:11:43,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll just confess everything.</i></font>

204
00:11:43,740 --> 00:11:44,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Be brave.</i></font>

205
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:55,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I know he'll hear me out. 
I don't care if it gets me killed.</i></font>

206
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:08,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoops. Drank too much broth 
and gave myself a bellyache.</font>

207
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:09,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Harada-san!</font>

208
00:12:09,760 --> 00:12:12,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Nio. And Hayashi, too.</font>

209
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:15,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's Hasumukai-san?</font>

210
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:17,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? He's around here somewhere.</font>

211
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:19,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was with him a moment ago—</font>

212
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:23,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We think Serizawa-san 
is looking for Hasumukai-san.</font>

213
00:12:23,940 --> 00:12:25,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Serizawa?</font>

214
00:12:30,850 --> 00:12:31,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hasumukai!</font>

215
00:12:35,740 --> 00:12:36,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hasumukai!</font>

216
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:39,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Hang in there!</font>

217
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:42,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm a fool.</i></font>

218
00:12:42,870 --> 00:12:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey! It's me! Open your eyes!</font>

219
00:12:43,540 --> 00:12:49,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>These guys don't argue about 
the country or fight for their homes.</i></font>

220
00:12:46,930 --> 00:12:49,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey! Hey!</font>

221
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:51,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hasumukai! Breathe!</font>

222
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:51,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They don't care how they look.</i></font>

223
00:12:52,330 --> 00:12:56,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're dirty. They stink.
They're messy eaters.</i></font>

224
00:12:52,680 --> 00:12:56,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hasumukai! Hasumukai!</font>

225
00:12:56,500 --> 00:12:58,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey, Hasumukai!</font>

226
00:12:56,510 --> 00:12:58,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All they do is train with swords.</i></font>

227
00:12:59,810 --> 00:13:03,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hang in there! Hey! Hasumukai!</font>

228
00:12:59,820 --> 00:13:03,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I know why I couldn't run away.</i></font>

229
00:13:04,420 --> 00:13:05,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I mean...</i></font>

230
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:10,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It wasn't a bad life.</i></font>

231
00:13:12,310 --> 00:13:16,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So I'm a turncoat now? 
Could I be a worse spy?</i></font>

232
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:19,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You. Yes, you, boy.</font>

233
00:13:19,680 --> 00:13:22,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got a friendly look to you, boy.</font>

234
00:13:22,100 --> 00:13:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, boy, infiltrate their ranks 
and investigate.</font>

235
00:13:26,290 --> 00:13:30,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Boy, can't you find out something 
a little more useful?</font>

236
00:13:28,020 --> 00:13:29,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He did show concern for me,</i></font>

237
00:13:30,280 --> 00:13:33,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I guess he never did bother 
to learn my name.</i></font>

238
00:13:35,230 --> 00:13:37,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hasumukai! Hasumukai!</font>

239
00:13:38,140 --> 00:13:40,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have a message for your family?</font>

240
00:13:43,790 --> 00:13:44,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

241
00:13:45,950 --> 00:13:47,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't hear you.</font>

242
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:50,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Are you sure you didn't know all along?</i></font>

243
00:13:51,130 --> 00:13:54,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You knew and were waiting 
for me to come clean.</i></font>

244
00:13:56,970 --> 00:13:59,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Harada-san.</font>

245
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:06,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Harada-san!</font>

246
00:14:07,060 --> 00:14:10,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We found relevant documents 
among Hasumukai-san's things.</font>

247
00:14:11,210 --> 00:14:13,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems he was a Choshu spy.</font>

248
00:14:14,750 --> 00:14:15,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That doesn't matter.</font>

249
00:14:16,390 --> 00:14:17,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was a traitor.</font>

250
00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:18,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

251
00:14:19,460 --> 00:14:23,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He tried to become one of us. And we...</font>

252
00:14:24,780 --> 00:14:25,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Harada-san.</font>

253
00:14:35,890 --> 00:14:38,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wanted to speak 
with me alone, Niimi-san?</font>

254
00:14:42,490 --> 00:14:44,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me close the curtain on Serizawa.</font>

255
00:14:45,770 --> 00:14:47,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll finish things ourselves.</font>

256
00:14:48,370 --> 00:14:52,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You make it sound as though 
you're both going to leave us.</font>

257
00:14:54,720 --> 00:14:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I may...</font>

258
00:14:56,240 --> 00:15:01,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Niimi-san, what precisely <i>is</i> 
your relationship with Serizawa-san?</font>

259
00:15:01,970 --> 00:15:03,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were next-door neighbors.</font>

260
00:15:05,500 --> 00:15:06,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all?</font>

261
00:15:06,760 --> 00:15:07,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all.</font>

262
