<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#2a2c2d">Bylaws</font></b></font></font>

266
00:15:10,510 --> 00:15:10,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#2a2c2d">Bylaws</font></b></font></font>

267
00:15:10,640 --> 00:15:10,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#2a2c2d">Bylaws</font></b></font></font>

268
00:15:10,760 --> 00:15:10,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#2a2c2d">Bylaws</font></b></font></font>

269
00:15:10,890 --> 00:15:11,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#2a2c2d">Bylaws</font></b></font></font>

270
00:15:11,010 --> 00:15:12,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#2a2c2d">Bylaws</font></b></font></font>

271
00:15:11,240 --> 00:15:14,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yamanami, I want you to have this.</font>

272
00:15:15,910 --> 00:15:16,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our laws.</font>

273
00:15:17,730 --> 00:15:18,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Laws?</font>

274
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:21,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our ranks will keep growing.</font>

275
00:15:22,190 --> 00:15:25,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">New recruits will disrupt
 our organization.</font>

276
00:15:26,140 --> 00:15:31,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A rabble with no clear rules 
can't fight the evils of Kyoto.</font>

277
00:15:32,040 --> 00:15:37,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="34"><font face="Georgia"><b><font color="#2a2c2d">Bylaws</font></b></font></font></font>

278
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:37,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wrote down all I could think of, 
but it's still only a rough draft.</font>

279
00:15:37,950 --> 00:15:40,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yamanami, I want you to complete it.</font>

280
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:47,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Niimi-san.</font>

281
00:15:50,290 --> 00:15:52,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Serizawa lived next door.</i></font>

282
00:15:52,780 --> 00:15:55,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That really is all 
that brought us together.</i></font>

283
00:15:56,150 --> 00:16:00,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He was a samurai's fourth son. 
I was the kid of a lowly foot soldier.</i></font>

284
00:16:01,130 --> 00:16:05,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But the difference in our status 
didn't mean a thing to him.</i></font>

285
00:16:05,560 --> 00:16:07,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Iori!</font>

286
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:09,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tsuguji. What happened to your face?</font>

287
00:16:09,980 --> 00:16:14,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My dad walloped me! 
All I did was break his favorite vase!</font>

288
00:16:14,020 --> 00:16:15,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's team up and teach him a lesson!</font>

289
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:20,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How? Your dad's huge.</font>

290
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:23,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My three big brothers did it!</font>

291
00:16:23,160 --> 00:16:25,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And they got beat black and blue for it.</font>

292
00:16:25,600 --> 00:16:26,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'll kill you next time.</font>

293
00:16:30,050 --> 00:16:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess it's hopeless, huh?</font>

294
00:16:33,380 --> 00:16:34,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll ambush him.</font>

295
00:16:34,760 --> 00:16:35,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ambush</i> him?!</font>

296
00:16:36,160 --> 00:16:37,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With a double pitfall.</font>

297
00:16:37,490 --> 00:16:38,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A <i>double</i> one?</font>

298
00:16:42,270 --> 00:16:43,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'll be along any moment now.</font>

299
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:56,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He fell in!</font>

300
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:56,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have him!</font>

301
00:16:58,300 --> 00:16:59,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The second layer dropped!</font>

302
00:16:59,800 --> 00:17:01,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go!</font>

303
00:17:01,310 --> 00:17:03,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wear a basket! He'll recognize you!</font>

304
00:17:05,240 --> 00:17:07,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you? Is that you, Tsuguji?</font>

305
00:17:08,930 --> 00:17:10,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's on to us!</font>

306
00:17:10,010 --> 00:17:10,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run for it!</font>

307
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:14,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll pay for this!</font>

308
00:17:17,390 --> 00:17:20,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There! We sure showed him.</font>

309
00:17:20,430 --> 00:17:21,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was a blast!</font>

310
00:17:22,570 --> 00:17:24,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to brace for reprisals.</font>

311
00:17:24,530 --> 00:17:27,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With my brawn and your brains, 
no one can stop us.</font>

312
00:17:28,280 --> 00:17:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll hit the meeting hall next.</font>

313
00:17:30,790 --> 00:17:34,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The meeting hall? 
They've got a vicious dog there.</font>

314
00:17:34,390 --> 00:17:35,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the plan?</font>

315
00:17:35,490 --> 00:17:38,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff">Let me think. First...</font></font>

316
00:17:43,480 --> 00:17:47,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Niimi, where are the other guys?</font>

317
00:17:47,560 --> 00:17:49,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about the party?</font>

318
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:52,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There won't be a party. 
You're the only guest.</font>

319
00:17:52,740 --> 00:17:53,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah?</font>

320
00:17:53,980 --> 00:17:58,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How long has it been since 
we faced each other like this, Tsuguji?</font>

321
00:17:58,800 --> 00:17:59,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tsu—</font>

322
00:18:01,890 --> 00:18:06,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one's called me 
that name in eons, Iori.</font>

323
00:18:06,800 --> 00:18:13,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You reserved this whole room just 
to get me here? Talk about thorough.</font>

324
00:18:13,840 --> 00:18:15,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's end it already.</font>

325
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:22,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Records of damages to merchants and 
the wealthy, and of internal purges.</font>

326
00:18:22,960 --> 00:18:27,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The results of five murder investigations 
and five missing persons cases.</font>

327
00:18:27,970 --> 00:18:30,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suspect you had a hand in all of them.</font>

328
00:18:31,570 --> 00:18:35,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've said what you needed to say. 
The Miburo will be fine now.</font>

329
00:18:38,780 --> 00:18:45,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, now. You ought to know better 
than to bring a sword to a party.</font>

330
00:18:47,570 --> 00:18:48,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Face facts.</font>

331
00:18:49,780 --> 00:18:51,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our role is over.</font>

332
00:18:53,600 --> 00:18:55,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What will you do?</font>

333
00:18:56,600 --> 00:18:57,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Follow right behind you.</font>

334
00:19:02,720 --> 00:19:04,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Souls form spirals.</font>

335
00:19:05,280 --> 00:19:09,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People die and are reborn as babies, 
and the cycle repeats.</font>

336
00:19:10,220 --> 00:19:14,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to relive the same time
 forever if I can.</font>

337
00:19:15,190 --> 00:19:16,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

338
00:19:17,760 --> 00:19:19,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My views on life and death.</font>

339
00:19:19,320 --> 00:19:22,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be stupid. You only live once.</font>

340
00:19:22,450 --> 00:19:25,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I've done 
just what I wanted to do.</font>

341
00:19:25,530 --> 00:19:27,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want to end it?</font>

342
00:19:29,070 --> 00:19:30,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine.</font>

343
00:19:31,520 --> 00:19:32,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

344
00:19:33,550 --> 00:19:36,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Iori, you end it alone.</font>

345
00:19:36,380 --> 00:19:39,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you think an appeal 
to sentiment would move me?</font>

346
00:19:39,750 --> 00:19:43,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what makes you naïve. 
It's your weakness.</font>

347
00:19:44,030 --> 00:19:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Iori, you're going to 
perform seppuku here.</font>

348
00:19:47,740 --> 00:19:52,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll have no trouble killing you 
and making it look that way.</font>

349
00:19:55,120 --> 00:19:56,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you laughing at?</font>

350
00:19:57,720 --> 00:19:59,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those were good days.</font>

351
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:03,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Things were simple 
and easy to understand.</font>

352
00:20:05,200 --> 00:20:07,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But little by little, we grew up.</font>

353
00:20:07,660 --> 00:20:11,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Places changed. People changed.
The times changed, too.</font>

354
00:20:11,620 --> 00:20:13,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Things got complicated.</font>

355
00:20:14,220 --> 00:20:15,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on. Do it.</font>

356
00:20:15,810 --> 00:20:17,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want it to look like suicide?</font>

357
00:20:18,310 --> 00:20:20,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My inspectors are good at their jobs.</font>

358
00:20:20,790 --> 00:20:22,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They'll see through your ruse.</font>

359
00:20:23,680 --> 00:20:27,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kondo's group can't ignore 
the murder of a commander.</font>

360
00:20:27,890 --> 00:20:30,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They'll come for your life.</font>

361
00:20:30,160 --> 00:20:32,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Iori! Damn you!</font>

362
00:20:33,330 --> 00:20:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wouldn't it be more fun that way?</font>

363
00:20:37,450 --> 00:20:38,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

364
00:20:38,730 --> 00:20:42,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If Serizawa Kamo has to die, 
wouldn't he rather die fighting?</font>

365
00:20:43,300 --> 00:20:46,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't want to take a bullet 
like some nobody, do you?</font>

366
00:20:47,310 --> 00:20:52,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And illness? Old age? 
Out of the question.</font>

367
00:20:53,430 --> 00:20:58,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't we always like 
getting one over on people?</font>

368
00:21:06,960 --> 00:21:08,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll listen.</font>

369
00:21:08,320 --> 00:21:10,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me think. First...</font>

370
00:21:28,340 --> 00:21:33,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font size="40">The 
Ultimate
Duo</font></b></font></font>

371
00:21:33,530 --> 00:21:34,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nio!</font>

372
00:21:34,810 --> 00:21:35,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nio!</font>

373
00:21:36,300 --> 00:21:37,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hayashi-san?</font>

374
00:21:37,840 --> 00:21:40,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um...</font>

375
00:21:40,430 --> 00:21:41,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are we rushing to?</font>

376
00:21:42,300 --> 00:21:43,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Niimi-san.</font>

377
00:21:44,530 --> 00:21:45,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He took his own life.</font>

378
00:23:20,120 --> 00:23:25,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="TImes New Roman"><font size="26"><b>{\an8}Next time</b></font></font></font>

379
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:23,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is Hijikata Toshizo.</font>

380
00:23:24,020 --> 00:23:25,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Niimi performed seppuku.</font>

381
00:23:26,470 --> 00:23:29,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know why he did it 
or what went through his mind,</font>

382
00:23:30,320 --> 00:23:33,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but anyone can see who had a hand in it.</font>

383
00:23:34,360 --> 00:23:35,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to end this.</font>

384
00:23:36,010 --> 00:23:37,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no going back now.</font>

385
00:23:38,240 --> 00:23:42,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For what we're here to protect, 
and for the Miburo's banner of "sincerity,"</font>

386
00:23:42,960 --> 00:23:44,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we'll settle things with Serizawa.</font>

387
00:23:45,990 --> 00:23:48,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time: "Near Yet Far."</font>

388
00:23:47,150 --> 00:23:49,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><b><font size="40">Near 
Yet Far</font></b></font></font>

